children.subject:
The goal, at least as was told to summer instructors, was the have hiring done early this semester. I know CS10 is done, and I know others were discussing it.

I should add, I never checked the TA app myself, but TAs told me that it was supposed to be with the Spring TA apps.

It might just be easiest to ask instructors directly? Or email Dan Garcia.

I mean, I see that 61B posted an application on FB last week, but I don't recall seeing any notices about hiring for any other summer classes yet. Maybe I just missed all of it, but I'm confused as to how hiring is over if people like me never knew to apply in the first place.

Meanwhile, I've never been able to figure out who summer instructors are until right before summer classes actually start; where is this information released?
Er, the hiring website doesn't even have the TA application out yet. Isn't it usually later, like March or something?
